	   <tr><td colspan=2>This guy is a easy camp with only one or two drawbacks. First there is a Gnoll that wanders in to the area randomly it seems and secondly every once in awhile so does shaman rex'ren. those are the only negatives I could see. they are both in the 25 and up rnage I think so they do pose a risk but not much if you are carefull. The hermit spawns exactly three minutes aafter his last death. when he pops he will cast a damage shield but you can pull him before he casts it. I would highly recomend doing this as it will save you a lot of time sitting to heal or mana casting heals.<br>to pull him target him through the crack in the door or by using /target a_hermit and say &quot;kill you&quot; in any context, which can be very funny. Anyways have fun loot and exp from him is excellent as his spawn time is so short and he is always level 20.<br>&nbsp;<br>Rehunh 51 Mystic<br>Rutro Rorge 52 Pathfinder<br>Nameless</td></tr>
