	   <tr><td colspan=2>I found this guy very good to solo for a wizzy at 25.&nbsp;&nbsp;You may be able to do my tactic earlier as well.  I got a full level 25-26 and 100 pp in about 4.5 hours, with no deaths.<br>I sat with my back to the wall, inside the compound at the chimney end.  Whenever the hermit spawned I would see a message that he cast a damage shield.  I had a hot key set up  /target a_hermit  as soon as I saw the message I would click it and target him inside the house.  I would then chain cast shock of frost on him.  I could usually get two cast before he even gets out of the house.  Two more shock of frost or one mor shock of frost and a flameshock would kill him. (he has about 500 HP and hits for between 5 - 30) If he dies inside the house his corpse is just around the corner to the left form the chimney.  I kept gate and root memmed as every now and then a nasty would show up.  I would root it and TP out.  Then gate back in, I was bound at the entracne to the compound.<br><br>Hope this is usefull<br><br>Paenne Gyver (solar)<br>Wizzy 26<br>Karana Server<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
